{"tid":1188084,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"日本現《新世紀福音戰士》主題屋  月租只係$3200","createTime":"2019-06-06T04:49:21.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-06T11:00:17.000Z","uid":184679,"like":14,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"2b6bbac7df7500e7e36f8df753dea3743219557c","tid":1188084,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-06T04:49:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.menclub.hk/api.php?mod=objects.show&amp;object_id=346196\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.menclub.hk%2Fapi.php%3Fmod%3Dobjects.show%26object_id%3D346196&h=6bdff81e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n要搵間平靚正嘅單位租住唔容易，而要搵間有自己喜歡嘅動漫主題單位租住更加唔容易！日前日本網友 @000calimero000 喺網上發現到，一間位於日本群馬縣前橋市上新田町外表平平無奇嘅住宅，原來內裡充滿咗《新世紀福音戰士》主題裝修。由大門一步入玄關位望向左邊已經可以見到用上 EVA 咗設計嘅開放式廚房，不論廚櫃、抽油煙機位置都有 EVA 元素，而廚房旁嘅大門更有 EVA 基地紅字「入室」兩個字！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.menclub.hk/api.php?mod=objects.show&amp;object_id=346200\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.menclub.hk%2Fapi.php%3Fmod%3Dobjects.show%26object_id%3D346200&h=c530b71d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n一打開印有「入室」嘅大門原來內有乾坤！呢間係屋內兩個房間嘅其中一間，大門嘅另一面印有「出擊」二字，啫係當你步出房門已經可幻想自己係 EVA 內嘅動漫角色出擊迎戰「使徒」。房內所有牆身，以天花、地板都用上 EVA 元素設計，非常有 NERV 總部設計風格，其中面向房門嘅牆身用上黑紅色設計，並由牆壁延伸至天花，其餘牆壁就上灰色設計，而地板就用上工業風嘅鋼板設計。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.menclub.hk/api.php?mod=objects.show&amp;object_id=346199\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.menclub.hk%2Fapi.php%3Fmod%3Dobjects.show%26object_id%3D346199&h=33bce848&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.menclub.hk/api.php?mod=objects.show&amp;object_id=346201\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.menclub.hk%2Fapi.php%3Fmod%3Dobjects.show%26object_id%3D346201&h=7d8cd078&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n不過驚喜點止咁少，除咗由客廳步入房間會「嘩一聲」外，原來打開衣櫃門都一樣充滿 EVA 元素！原來衣櫃內印有 EVA 基地紅字「機密」兩個字，有網民笑指呢個單位係 NERV 群馬縣分部。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.menclub.hk/api.php?mod=objects.show&amp;object_id=346197\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.menclub.hk%2Fapi.php%3Fmod%3Dobjects.show%26object_id%3D346197&h=d3639f7b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n屋內主題房間只有一個，另一房間用上普通裝修，適合 EVA Fans 與唔係 Fans 嘅友人一同租住，不過呢個單位月租連管理費都只係45,000 yen，一個人畀都可以負擔得起。全屋面積441呎，分別有一個洗手間及開放式廚房，並設有兩個房間，其中一個就係上文介紹嘅 EVA 主題房。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.menclub.hk/hobby/20413\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.menclub.hk%2Fhobby%2F20413&d=M59wMjr1KB2wSFKn0iQ%2BgtB4iDtRAy51VXy1YCRVmoY%3D&h=56d6dfe1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.menclub.hk/hobby/20413</a>"},{"pid":"a8c6e23095974290a58da5b18d4ae7b9c32b3121","tid":1188084,"uid":53687,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-06T04:52:16.000Z","msg":"包唔包綾波麗同明日香先？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2b37afb714163222b7fff4c82e898025b29570d2","tid":1188084,"uid":196924,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-06T04:57:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />呢啲位除非你本身喺附近住同返工，否則啱退休<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n賣豆腐就啱晒，九個字車程到五連髮夾彎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"90fee1c66217aca6a12babea1331d61e0a7c9e09","tid":1188084,"uid":184679,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-06T04:59:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://gss0.baidu.com/7Po3dSag_xI4khGko9WTAnF6hhy/zhidao/pic/item/b219ebc4b74543a9b5d8731f15178a82b8011425.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgss0.baidu.com%2F7Po3dSag_xI4khGko9WTAnF6hhy%2Fzhidao%2Fpic%2Fitem%2Fb219ebc4b74543a9b5d8731f15178a82b8011425.jpg&h=05f67461&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"7c584cb9d5312cd1fa94b1be562788018faef17a","tid":1188084,"uid":188310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-06T05:01:44.000Z","msg":"想屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"55e0a1928d5a33ab9f284529ce841bd